snippet.title: Trancelation - Early Access Teaser
snippet.description:
Trancelation is a neon arcade game about language learning and it's now available on Steam Early Access here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/716560/Trancelation/

About Trancelation:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/716560/Trancelation/ 
Presskit: http://files.mythicowl.com/sCF52FZ 
Website: http://www.mythicowl.com/trancelation/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/trancelation/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/trancelat

About MythicOwl:
MythicOwl, established in 2014 by Tomasz Mularczyk, is an indie development company focused on bringing educational value to its games.
Website: www.mythicowl.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MythicOwl/ 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/MythicOwlGames
